From d1e23ef176fc6b6ec881bbd141ba8ef46a450f1f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pier Luigi Fiorini <pierluigi.fiorini@liri.io>
Date: Sun, 28 Feb 2021 22:11:51 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 4/5] Restart the greeter only on crash

Keep the greeter process alive and switch to its VT instead of
restarting it, when the user session is finished.

This makes it for a very fast switch to the greeter and easier
management.
